---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Copenhagen MedTech's privacy policy. How we handle your data."
>
  <div class="privacy">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="privacy__updated">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>
      Copenhagen MedTech is a student-led non-profit organisation. This privacy policy explains how we collect,
      use, and protect information when you use our website at cphmedtech.dk.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      We collect minimal data. When you use our contact form, the information you provide (name, email, message)
      is sent via your email client. We do not store form submissions on our servers.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      This website does not use cookies or tracking scripts. We do not use Google Analytics
      or any third-party analytics services.
    </p>

    <h2>External Links</h2>
    <p>
      Our website contains links to external services (LinkedIn, Instagram, Facebook, event registration).
      These services have their own privacy policies. We are not responsible for their practices.
    </p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
      Under GDPR, you have the right to access, correct, or delete any personal data we hold.
      Since we collect minimal data, this primarily applies to any emails you've sent us directly.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy-related questions, contact us at
      <a href="mailto:hello@cphmedtech.dk">hello@cphmedtech.dk</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>

<style lang="scss">
  @use '../styles/tokens' as *;

  .privacy {
    max-width: 40rem;

    h1 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    h2 { margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 1.25rem; }
    p { color: $color-fg-muted; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    a { color: $color-primary; text-decoration: underline; }
  }

  .privacy__updated {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: $color-fg-muted;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
</style>
